WEBVTT

00:01:28.700 --> 00:01:31.580
Mirov helwestên hev teqlîd dikin.

00:01:31.580 --> 00:01:33.380
Ku hûn cem yekî

00:01:33.380 --> 00:01:36.000
lingê xwe li ser hev re avêtî bin,

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:38.458
hûn ê jî wisa bikin.

00:01:38.780 --> 00:01:41.220
Ji ber ku em

00:01:41.224 --> 00:01:43.031
hertim teqlîd dikin,

00:01:43.031 --> 00:01:44.891
bawişk jî tê teqlîd kirin.

00:01:44.900 --> 00:01:47.180
Gorî zanista

00:01:47.188 --> 00:01:50.054
"bandora mergîsê"

00:01:50.060 --> 00:01:52.481
bi hin noronên neynik mimkûn e.

00:01:52.800 --> 00:01:55.580
Noronên neynik hûcreyên mêjî ne.

00:01:55.580 --> 00:01:58.140
Tevgerê, heke em bikin

00:01:58.146 --> 00:01:59.806
an yekê din bike

00:01:59.806 --> 00:02:01.500
ev hûcre wek hev dixebitin.